data.description: Welcome to the Estates at Verona Trace! 2019 Majestic Model w /3 car garage! LOW HOA! Fantastic opportunity for friends/family to become your neighbor! Home next door is available! MLS #275352! Chef's dream! Complete w/stylish island-prepare culinary delights while entertaining family/friends! Ceramic tile adds elegance & easy to maintain. Lovely lake views/sunsets on large patio-creating tranquil atmosphere to help you unwind after a long day. Equipped w/Solar Panels for low electric! Near I95/shopping/restaurants! Community clubhouse/pool/tennis. Embark on a life filled w/ luxury & serenity!
